data.description: Your Perfect Two-Family Home has come to market! This property is ideal for Investors, fully occupied, tenants' rents are up to date and can be improved to market value. There has been attention to detail in all renovations and maintenance. Both units have large eat-in-kitchens, a full series of well-appointed cabinets and there is open space in each kitchen offering additional storage with direct access to the fenced backyard. Newer hot water heaters, efficient furnaces and meters allowing tenants to pay their own utilities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your own. Schedule a showing today and picture the possibilities!
